div.p:
I adore Thee, O obedient Child Jesus, in Thy exact
compliance with the commands of Mary and Joseph;
give me the grace joyfully to obey my superiors.

(In whose hands are iniquities;
their right hand
is filled with gifts.)

Suscitans a terra inopem,
* et de stercore erigens
pauperem;
